---
import { createUrl } from '../utils/urls';
---

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.2/css/all.min.css" />
  <title>Come acquistare da Mondo Bimbo - Lista Nascita Leone</title>
</head>

<div class="header">
  <a href={createUrl('/lista-nascita')} class="btn-back">
    <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-left"></i>
    Torna alla Lista
  </a>
</div>

<h1 class="main-title"><span class="rainbow-text">Come regalare da Mondo Bimbo</span></h1>

<div class="content-container">
  <div class="instruction-card">
    <div class="icon-header">
      <i class="fa-solid fa-phone"></i>
      <h2>Procedura di acquisto</h2>
    </div>
    
    <div class="steps">
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-number">1</div>
        <div class="step-content">
          <h3>Puoi chiamare o contattare tramite Whatsapp i numeri</h3>
          <p class="phone-number">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-phone"></i>
            <strong>0761777974 o 3664583200</strong>
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="step-content">
          <h3>Puoi andare direttamente al negozio Mondo Bimbo Store</h3>
          <p class="phone-number">
            <strong>Strada San Lazzaro Viterbo (Parco Commerciale San Lazzaro)</strong>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-number">2</div>
        <div class="step-content">
          <h3>Richiedi la Lista Nascita</h3>
          <p class="highlight-text">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-baby"></i>
            "Chiedi della lista nascita per <strong>Leone</strong> a nome Rapiti -  Papalini"
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-number">3</div>
        <div class="step-content">
          <h3>Scegli il prodotto</h3>
          <p>Indica al personale quale prodotto ti interessa dalla lista.</p>
          <p>Ti confermeranno disponibilità, prezzo aggiornato e modalità di pagamento.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-number">4</div>
        <div class="step-content">
          <h3>Accordati per il ritiro/consegna</h3>
          <p>Stabilisci insieme al personale:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Modalità di pagamento</li>
            <li>Tempi</li>
            <li>Ritiro in negozio o consegna (possiamo ritirare anche noi)</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="info-box">
      <i class="fa-solid fa-info-circle"></i>
      <div>
        <h4>Informazioni utili</h4>
        <p>Lo staff di Mondo Bimbo è molto disponibile e ti aiuterà in tutto il processo. Potrai anche chiedere consigli o altre foto sui prodotti in lista o fuori lista!</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="back-to-list">
      <a href={createUrl('/lista-nascita')} class="btn-primary">
        <i class="fa-solid fa-list"></i>
        Torna alla Lista Nascita
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style is:global>
  body {
    background: url('../images/background.png') center center/cover no-repeat fixed;
    min-height: 100vh;
    font-family: system-ui, Arial, sans-serif, "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji", "Noto Color Emoji";
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 1rem;
    margin: 0;
    position: relative;
  }
  
  /* Overlay per migliorare la leggibilità */
  body::before {
    content: '';
    position: fixed;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
    z-index: -1;
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  
  .header {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 10;
    padding: 1rem 2rem;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 900px;
  }
  
  .btn-back {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    padding: 0.8rem 1.5rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #388e3c, #4caf50);
    color: white;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    font-weight: bold;
    font-size: 1rem;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(56, 142, 60, 0.3);
  }
  
  .btn-back:hover {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2e7d32, #388e3c);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(56, 142, 60, 0.4);
  }
  
  .main-title {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 3.5rem;
    font-weight: bold;
    margin: 1rem 0 2rem 0;
    color: #333;
    text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 10;
  }
  
  .rainbow-text {
    background: linear-gradient(45deg, 
      #ff0000, #ff8c00, #ffd700, #32cd32, 
      #1e90ff, #8a2be2, #ff1493, #ff0000);
    background-size: 400% 400%;
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    animation: rainbow-flow 3s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  
  @keyframes rainbow-flow {
    0% {
      background-position: 0% 50%;
    }
    50% {
      background-position: 100% 50%;
    }
    100% {
      background-position: 0% 50%;
    }
  }
  
  /* Responsive per il titolo */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .main-title {
      font-size: 2.2rem;
      margin: 1rem 0 1.5rem 0;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
    }
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .main-title {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      margin: 0.5rem 0 1rem 0;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    }
  }
  
  .content-container {
    max-width: 800px;
    width: 100%;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 1rem;
  }
  
  .instruction-card {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
    border: 2px solid #388e3c;
    border-radius: 1.5rem;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    padding: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  
  .icon-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    color: #388e3c;
  }
  
  .icon-header i {
    font-size: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    display: block;
  }
  
  .icon-header h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin: 0;
    font-weight: bold;
  }
  
  .steps {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  
  .step {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 1rem;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    background: rgba(76, 175, 80, 0.05);
    border-radius: 1rem;
    border-left: 4px solid #4caf50;
  }
  
  .step-number {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
    background: #4caf50;
    color: white;
    border-radius: 50%;
    font-weight: bold;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  
  .step-content h3 {
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0;
    color: #2e7d32;
    font-size: 1.3rem;
  }
  
  .step-content p {
    margin: 0.5rem 0;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: #555;
  }
  
  .phone-number {
    background: #e8f5e8;
    padding: 1rem;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    border: 1px solid #4caf50;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    text-align: center;
  }
  
  .phone-number i {
    color: #4caf50;
    margin-right: 0.5rem;
  }
  
  .highlight-text {
    background: #fff3e0;
    padding: 1rem;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    border: 1px solid #ff9800;
    font-style: italic;
  }
  
  .highlight-text i {
    color: #ff9800;
    margin-right: 0.5rem;
  }
  
  .step-content ul {
    margin: 0.5rem 0;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
  }
  
  .step-content li {
    margin: 0.3rem 0;
    color: #555;
  }
  
  .info-box {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 1rem;
    background: #e3f2fd;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    border: 1px solid #2196f3;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  
  .info-box i {
    color: #2196f3;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 0.2rem;
  }
  
  .info-box h4 {
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0;
    color: #1976d2;
  }
  
  .info-box p {
    margin: 0;
    color: #555;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  
  .back-to-list {
    text-align: center;
  }
  
  .btn-primary {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    padding: 1rem 2rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff9800, #f57c00);
    color: white;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    font-weight: bold;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(255, 152, 0, 0.3);
  }
  
  .btn-primary:hover {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f57c00, #ef6c00);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(255, 152, 0, 0.4);
  }
  
  /* Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .content-container {
      padding: 0 0.5rem;
    }
    
    .instruction-card {
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }
    
    .step {
      flex-direction: column;
      text-align: center;
      gap: 1rem;
    }
    
    .step-number {
      align-self: center;
    }
    
    .icon-header h2 {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }
    
    .icon-header i {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
    }
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .instruction-card {
      padding: 1rem;
    }
    
    .step {
      padding: 1rem;
    }
    
    .step-content h3 {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
    }
    
    .btn-primary {
      padding: 0.8rem 1.5rem;
      font-size: 1rem;
    }
  }
</style>
